Class Transport

  • java.lang.Object
    • Vehicle
      • Transport
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Movable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Ferry, Trailer

    public abstract class Transport
extends Vehicle

    Transport

    Subclass to vehicle, capable of loading cars (excluding Scania) onto its ramp and moving them around. Has 2 subclasses, Ferry and Trailer.
